{"title":"堆雪人（外一首）","authors":["郭伟"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":2,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆雪人（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大片大片的雪花冻僵了村庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也冻僵了鸟儿的翅膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻僵的村庄里蹦出了一伙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有冻僵的孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用他们的天真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆着冬爷爷的塑像。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们向冬爷爷笑着，跳着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嬉戏在一个洁白的童话里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个冬天孕着温暖的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火炉子傍没有的春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也没有发现，隔窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝望的还有一颗成熟了的童心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和他那飞翔着的思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是抛雪球的孩子中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又多了一双诗人的手掌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——致一位远方朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思念应该是圆圆的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆圆的象十五的月亮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗憾的是你带走了一半，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另一半挂在我的心上。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}